Stoffer, D. S., & Wall, K. D. (1991). Bootstrapping state-space
models: Gaussian maximum likelihood estimation and the
Kalman filter. Journal of the American Statistical
Association, 86(416), 1024–1033. https://doi.org/10.1080/01621459.1991.10475148
